#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:4
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:6
msgid ""
"Scenes are a way to organize your work. Each blend-file can contain multiple scenes, which share other data such "
"as objects and materials."
msgstr "场景是组织作品的一种方法。每个blend文件都可以包含多个场景，这些场景共享物体或者材质等其他数据。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:9
msgid ""
"Scene management and library appending/linking are based on Blender's :doc:`Library and Data System </"
"data_system/index>`, so it is a good idea to read that manual page first, if you are not familiar with the "
"basics of that system."
msgstr ""
"场景管理和库的追加和关联基于Blender的 :doc:`库和数据系统 </data_system/index>` 。如果你不熟悉该系统，最好去阅读下"
"相关的手册知识。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:16
msgid "Scene data-block menu."
msgstr "场景数据块菜单"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:18
msgid "You can select and create scenes with the *Scene data-block* menu in the *Info Editor* header."
msgstr "用户可以使用 *信息编辑器* 标题栏中的 *场景数据块* 菜单选择和创建场景。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:22
msgid "Controls"
msgstr "控件"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:24
msgid "Scenes"
msgstr "场景"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:25
msgid "A list of available scenes."
msgstr "可用场景列表。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:63
msgid "Add ``+``"
msgstr "添加 ``+``"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:27
msgid "New"
msgstr "新建"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:28
msgid "Creates an empty scene with default values."
msgstr "使用默认值新建一个空的场景。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:30
msgid "Copy Settings"
msgstr "拷贝设置"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:30
msgid "Creates an empty scene, but also copies the settings from the active scene into the new one."
msgstr "使用当前活动场景的设置，新建一个空场景。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:37
msgid "Link Objects"
msgstr "关联物体"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:33
msgid ""
"This option creates a new scene with the same settings and contents as the active scene. However, instead of "
"copying the objects, the new scene contains links to the objects in the old scene. Therefore, changes to objects "
"in the new scene will result in the same changes to the original scene, because the objects used are literally "
"the same. The reverse is also true."
msgstr ""
"此选项会使用活动场景的设置和内容创建一个新的场景。然而，与复制物体的区别是，新场景的物体都是关联旧场景对应物体"
"的。因此，新场景中物体的改动都会反映到旧场景，因为所使用的物体本质是相同的。反之亦然。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:48
msgid "Link Object Data"
msgstr "关联物体数据"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:40
msgid ""
"Creates new, duplicate copies of all of the objects in the currently selected scene, but each one of those "
"duplicate objects will have links to the object-data (meshes, materials and so on) of the corresponding objects "
"in the original scene."
msgstr "为当前选中的场景中所有物体创建副本，但是每个副本保持对原场景对应物体数据(网格, 材质等等) 的关联。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:44
msgid ""
"This means that you can change the position, orientation and size of the objects in the new scene without "
"affecting other scenes, but any modifications to the object-data (meshes, materials, etc.) will also affect "
"other scenes. This is because a single instance of the \"object-data\" is now being shared by all of the objects "
"in all of the scenes, that link to it. This has the effect of making a new independent copy of the object-data."
msgstr ""
"这意味着，可以改变新场景中物体的位置、方向和大小，而不会影响到其它场景。但是任何对物体数据（网格，材质等）的修改"
"都会影响到其它场景。这是因为所有的场景的物体关联的是同一 *物体数据* 实例。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:54
msgid "Full Copy"
msgstr "完整复制"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:51
msgid ""
"Using this option, nothing is shared. This option creates a fully independent scene with copies of the active "
"scene's contents. Every object in the original scene is duplicated, and a duplicate, private copy of its object-"
"data is made as well."
msgstr "此选项会创建一个活动场景的独立副本，不会共享任何数据。复制场景物体的同时，也会复制其物体数据。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:58
msgid ""
"To choose between these options, it is useful to understand the difference between *Object* and *Object Data*. "
"See :doc:`Duplication </editors/3dview/object/editing/duplication>`."
msgstr ""
"理解物体和物体数据之间的差异，有助于在这些选项中做出恰当选择。参考 :doc:`复制 </editors/3dview/object/editing/"
"duplication>`."

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:62
msgid ""
"The choices for adding a scene, therefore, determine just how much of this information will be *copied from* the "
"active scene to the new one, and how much will be *shared* (linked)."
msgstr "新增场景方式的选择，决定了哪些信息会从活动场景 *复制* 到新场景，哪些信息是 *共享* (关联)的。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:67
msgid "Delete ``X``"
msgstr "删除 ``X``"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:66
msgid "You can delete the current scene by clicking the *X* next to the name in the Info Editor."
msgstr "在信息编辑器中，点击场景名字旁边的 *X* 按钮可以删除当前场景。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:69
msgid "Linking to a Scene"
msgstr "关联到一个场景"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes/introduction.rst:71
msgid "You can :ref:`link <data-system-linked-libraries-make-link>` any object from one scene to another."
msgstr "用户可以将一个场景的任意物体 :ref:`关联 <data-system-linked-libraries-make-link>` 到另一场景。"
